  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  female with rheumatoid arthritis

          -  Disease activity scores &gt; 2.6

          -  use of anti-TNF-alpha drugs for at least 8 weeks

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMD &lt; 20 kg/m2

          -  fibromyalgia

          -  cardiovascular disease
      </textblock>
